(1, 'aboutus', 'About Eagle news', '<font color=\"#7b8898\" face=\"Mercury SSm A, Mercury SSm B, Georgia, Times, Times New Roman, Microsoft YaHei New, Microsoft Yahei, å¾®è½¯é›…é»‘, å®‹ä½“, SimSun, STXihei, åŽæ–‡ç»†é»‘, serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 26px;\"> \r\n\r\n<br>\r\nWelcome to Eagle News, your trusted source for timely, reliable, and insightful news coverage. At Eagle News, we are driven by our unwavering commitment to delivering the latest news, in-depth analysis, and compelling stories that matter most to you.\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nWho We Are\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nEagle News is more than just a news outlet; we are a team of dedicated journalists and professionals with a passion for journalism\'s core values: truth, integrity, and objectivity. With years of experience in the field, our team brings a wealth of expertise to the forefront of the news industry.\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nOur Mission\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nOur mission at Eagle News is clear: to empower you with accurate, balanced, and comprehensive news coverage. We strive to keep you informed, foster a deeper understanding of the world, and spark meaningful conversations that shape our society.\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nWhy Choose Eagle News\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrustworthiness: We uphold the highest standards of journalistic integrity, providing you with news you can trust.<br>\r\nDiversity: Our commitment to diverse perspectives ensures a well-rounded view of current events and issues.<br>\r\nAccessibility: Stay connected with our news updates across multiple platforms, ensuring you\'re always in the know.<br>\r\nEngagement: We value your insights and feedback. Join our community, and let\'s engage in meaningful discussions.\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGet in Touch\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nWe appreciate your visit to Eagle News. If you have questions, story ideas, or feedback, please don\'t hesitate to reach out. You can connect with us through our website, social media channels, or email, and become an integral part of our news community.\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThank you for choosing Eagle News as your source for news and information. Together, let\'s stay informed and make a difference in our world.\r\n\r\n</span></font><br>', '2023-09-13 18:30:00', '2023-09-13 18:57:13'),
